Didn’t seek it, didn’t choose it.
But it’s up to me to use it.
I must suffer if I lose it. 
Give an account if I abuse it.
Just a tiny little minute, but eternity is in it.”

“We must see that our troops, veterans & their families have the support they need. Together, I know we can get the job done.” #CMFCSummit

“We cannot forget the families they leave behind sacrifice just as much as our heroes who deploy on missions for our country.” #CMFCSummit
“My father-in-law served in the U.S. military for several years and my wife was a military child.” #CMFCSummit
“Whenever I meet with military families, two people who frequently come to mind are my father-in-law and my wife.” #CMFCSummit
